OL,3,CParts of UK may get 'brief respite'
OL,4,Cfrom scorching weather
OL,6,FLight rain and clouds are possible in
OL,7,Fparts of the UK as the country
OL,8,Fswelters in another heatwave with
OL,9,Femergency services warning of
OL,10,F"extreme" wildfire risks.
OL,12,FThe Met Office said it will be windy
OL,13,Fin some places on Monday with cooler
OL,14,Ftemperatures in the east, but warm
OL,15,Ftemperatures in the west.
OL,17,FParts of the country might be hit with
OL,18,Fa little rain, but the forecaster said
OL,19,Fthe scorching conditions experienced
OL,20,Fby much of the UK are due to last into
OL,21,Fthe coming week.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@IO]
