OL,3,CParts of UK may get 'brief respite'
OL,4,Cfrom scorching weather
OL,6,FMeteorologist Honor Criswick said:
OL,7,F"For the time being it looks like the
OL,8,Fheatwave is set to continue, but
OL,9,Fdepending on where you are, there may
OL,10,Fbe a brief respite in the heat to
OL,11,Fcome."
OL,13,FNatural England's Fire Severity Index
OL,14,Fhas put much of England at "very high"
OL,15,Frisk of wildfires, with some areas in
OL,16,Fsouthern England and the Midlands at
OL,17,F"exceptional" risk.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@FO]vD@\OUvD@fO]yD@AOUyD@MO]
