OL,3,CParts of UK may get 'brief respite'
OL,4,Cfrom scorching weather
OL,6,FDerbyshire Fire and Rescue has been
OL,7,Fcalled out to two moorland wildfires
OL,8,Fin recent days while London Fire
OL,9,FBrigade (LFB) dealt with a blaze
OL,10,Finvolving shrubbery at Stratford
OL,11,FStation on Friday evening, which
OL,12,Fcaused rail line closures.
OL,14,FAssistant Commissioner Tom Goodall
OL,15,Fsaid there had been no injuries from
OL,16,Fthe fire, but rail disruption was
OL,17,Fexpected to continue into the morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
