OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783959567
OL,3,CParts of UK may get 'brief respite'
OL,4,Cfrom scorching weather
OL,6,F"We have worked with the local
OL,7,Fauthority and our other partners to
OL,8,Fset up two rest centres for residents
OL,9,Fwho have been evacuated from their
OL,10,Fhomes," he said.
OL,12,F"They are all being supported at this
OL,13,Ftime and we are hopeful that the
OL,14,Fmajority of them will be able to
OL,15,Freturn home tonight."
OL,17,FThe LFB confirmed one house was
OL,18,Falight, while the gardens of around 30
OL,19,Fproperties were also affected.
