OL,3,CParts of UK may get 'brief respite'
OL,4,Cfrom scorching weather
OL,6,FEast Sussex Fire and Rescue Service
OL,7,Fwas called to a "large fire in the
OL,8,Fopen" on the South Downs near
OL,9,FEastbourne on Saturday, while teams
OL,10,Falso tackled a blaze at Devil's Dyke
OL,11,Fin South Downs National Park in West
OL,12,FSussex.
OL,14,FDave Swallow, National Fire Chiefs
OL,15,FCouncil (NFCC) wildfire deputy lead
OL,16,Fand lead tactical adviser, warned that
OL,17,Fthe dry, sunny and hot conditions
OL,18,F"significantly increase wildfire risk".
OL,26,@oD@QOUpD@EO]zD@AOUzD@fO]
