OL,3,CParts of UK may get 'brief respite'
OL,4,Cfrom scorching weather
OL,6,FThe Met Office has revealed that
OL,7,Frecord-breaking temperatures have led
OL,8,Fto 2026 becoming the first year to
OL,9,Frecord 35C on six separate days.
OL,11,FThis broke the previous record set in
OL,12,F1976 and 2020 when five days were
OL,13,Frecorded with temperatures over 35C.
OL,15,FThis year is also the first to see
OL,16,Ftemperatures of 35C or higher in three
OL,17,Fcalendar months, and broke the record
OL,18,Ffor most temperatures of 34C or
OL,19,Fhigher, with nine so far this summer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
