OL,3,CParts of UK may get 'brief respite'
OL,4,Cfrom scorching weather
OL,6,FDerbyshire Constabulary announced that
OL,7,Fthe body of an 18-year-old man had
OL,8,Fbeen recovered from the water near a
OL,9,Fweir at the Darley Abbey Mills complex
OL,10,Fafter two teenagers got into
OL,11,Fdifficulty.
OL,13,FGreater Manchester Police said an 18-
OL,14,Fyear-old male died at Dovestone
OL,15,FReservoir, Oldham, on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
